Text:
@AArelig: Works perfectly on mine, try to remove the songs from the iPod, resync, then add the songs back to the iPod and see if that fixes the issue.

If it doesn't, I recommend removing the songs from iTunes, Sync the iPod (to remove the songs from the iPod), then re-add the songs to iTunes.

If all else fails, re-download torrent or try restoring your iPod
